CLASSIC COCKTAILS
WITH A MODERN TWIST
in Downtown Pensacola, Florida.
Photos by MOVE MEDIA
The Kennedy melds together the nostalgia of the mid-century with a twist of the modern era. Classic Cocktails reign king, but our knowledgeable bartenders create thoughtful and carefully crafted drinks for an innovative tasting experience.
The kitchen features small bites to coincide with our cocktails. You’ll find vegetarian and meat lover options alike.
After you visit us, please stop in to our sister bar, Old Hickory Whiskey Bar, a few blocks south at 123 South Palafox Place.
1 South Palafox Place   Pensacola, FL 32502

SUN-THURS
4pm – 12am
